column14: As someone with fine, thinning, wispy hair, I've experimented with a number of shampoos that promise to deliver thicker, fuller-looking locks. This one actually spotlights that claim in the brand name, and I feel it delivers pretty well on its promise. While it hasn't actually added more strands or made the existing ones thicker, it *has* given my limp locks more body by gently cleaning my hair without weighing it down.
